    "content": "<html>\n<head>\n    <title>Amortized Analysis</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            background-color: #f0f0f0;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .button-container {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .button {\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            background-color: #4CAF50;\n            color: #fff;\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n        .button:hover {\n            background-color: #3e8e41;\n        }\n        .slider-container {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .slider {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .slider input[type=\"range\"] {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .slider input[type=\"range\"]::-webkit-slider-thumb {\n            -webkit-appearance: none;\n            appearance: none;\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .slider input[type=\"range\"]::-moz-range-thumb {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .slider input[type=\"range\"]::-ms-thumb {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .slider label {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .slider label:hover {\n            background-color: #ccc;\n        }\n        .button-container input[type=\"submit\"] {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .button-container input[type=\"submit\"]:hover {\n            background-color: #3e8e41;\n        }\n        .text {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>Amortized Analysis</h1>\n        <div class=\"button-container\">\n            <button class=\"button\" onclick=\"calculate()\">Calculate</button>\n            <button class=\"button\" onclick=\"save()\">Save</button>\n            <button class=\"button\" onclick=\"clear()\">Clear</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"slider-container\">\n            <label for=\"amount\">Amount:</label>\n            <input type=\"range\" id=\"amount\" min=\"1\" max=\"10000\" value=\"1000\" onChange=\"calculate()\">\n            <span id=\"amount-value\"></span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"slider-container\">\n            <label for=\"rate\">Rate:</label>\n            <input type=\"range\" id=\"rate\" min=\"0.1\" max=\"10\" value=\"1\" onChange=\"calculate()\">\n            <span id=\"rate-value\"></span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"slider-container\">\n            <label for=\"duration\">Duration:</label>\n            <input type=\"range\" id=\"duration\" min=\"1\" max=\"1000\" value=\"10\" onChange=\"calculate()\">\n            <span id=\"duration-value\"></span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"text\">\n        <p>Amortized Analysis is a method of calculating the present value of a future amount based on the future value of an investment or loan.</p>\n        <p>It takes into account the interest rate and duration of the investment or loan to estimate the present value.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        let amount = 0;\n        let rate = 0;\n        let duration = 0;\n\n        function calculate() {\n            amount = parseInt(document.getElementById('amount').value);\n            rate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('rate').value);\n            duration = parseInt(document.getElementById('duration').value);\n\n            let presentValue = 0;\n\n            for (let i = 0; i < duration; i++) {\n                presentValue += amount * (1 + rate / 100) ** i;\n            }\n\n            document.getElementById('amount-value').innerHTML = 'Present Value: $' + presentValue.toFixed(2);\n        }\n\n        function save() {\n            localStorage.setItem('amount', amount);\n            localStorage.setItem('rate', rate);\n            localStorage.setItem('duration', duration);\n        }\n\n        function clear() {\n            amount = 0;\n            rate = 0;\n            duration = 0;\n            document.getElementById('amount-value').innerHTML = 'Present Value: $0.00';\n        }\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"
